I feel like now

00:47:02.179 --> 00:47:04.179
after we were talking about that, I should be like,

00:47:04.179 --> 00:47:06.179
actually, I really like internal

00:47:06.399 --> 00:47:08.399
R packages that people have developed at

00:47:08.399 --> 00:47:10.399
companies I've worked for.

00:47:10.399 --> 00:47:12.399
They're not publicly available, but

00:47:12.399 --> 00:47:14.399
people in my team at BMS developed

00:47:14.399 --> 00:47:16.399
R packages that were used

