I guess

00:47:24.399 --> 00:47:26.399
what would be a publicly

00:47:26.399 --> 00:47:28.399
available R package that would be my favorite?

00:47:28.399 --> 00:47:30.399
I like

00:47:30.399 --> 00:47:32.399
all my internal R packages, but

00:47:32.399 --> 00:47:34.399
I don't know.

00:47:34.620 --> 00:47:36.620
That's a really hard one.

00:47:36.620 --> 00:47:38.620
Probably if I did an analysis

00:47:38.620 --> 00:47:40.620
of what I actually use, it's

00:47:40.620 --> 00:47:42.620
dplyr and ggplot2,

00:47:42.620 --> 00:47:44.620
like everybody.

00:47:44.620 --> 00:47:46.620
I guess that.

00:47:46.620 --> 00:47:48.620
Awesome.

00:47:48.620 --> 00:47:50.620
Thank you.

